
Ranger Help for: enemy reptile
==============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing reptile means your Ranger specializes against snakes, lizards,
crocodiles, turtles, and other cold-blooded scaled creatures.

This is useful across swamps, deserts, jungles, beaches, plains,
mountains, and underground areas.

COMMAND:
  setenemy reptile

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
